snippet.title: Amber Hagerman: The History Behind the Amber Alert
snippet.description:
Young Amber Hagerman of Texas was abducted and killed in 1996 and the case remains unsolved. 

But the AMBER Alert, created after her death, has helped save hundreds of children. 

On this special edition of DBL's True Crime Chronicles, we take you back to where it began and explain how AMBER Alerts came about. Our story includes exclusive content from TEGNA's WFAA-TV in Dallas.
